prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card, dreamy fantasy art style. A surreal and humorous landscape where interests come to life. In the center, cartoon illustrated versions of Jordan and Lao Lao from the reference photo are snowboarding down a fluffy, cloud-like mountain under a pastel sky with soft, glowing binary code (0s and 1s) floating like gentle snowflakes. Jordan, wearing his dark t-shirt, is on a snowboard shaped like a giant piece of nigiri sushi. Lao Lao, in her white jacket, is on a snowboard that looks like a perfectly marbled slice of wagyu steak. They are both laughing joyfully. The snowy landscape below them is a fantastical food paradise: the ground is made of fried rice, evergreen trees are actually stalks of broccoli, and a whimsical river of soy sauce flows through the scene, carrying little dumpling boats. The text "Happy Birthday, Jordan" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script in a complementary color, positioned safely in the sky area. The overall atmosphere is magical, ethereal, lighthearted, and vibrant.
